<p>It that possible to play online audio streaming or mp3 from playground with swift ?</p>  <p>For example, here is the swift code to play online mp3 </p>  <pre><code>    var player = AVPlayer()     let url = "http://www.nasa.gov/mp3/640149main_Computers%20are%20in%20Control.mp3"     let playerItem = AVPlayerItem( URL:NSURL( string:url.stringByAddingPercentEscapesUsingEncoding(NSUTF8StringEncoding)! )!)     player = AVPlayer(playerItem:playerItem)     player.rate = 1.0;     player.play() </code></pre>